Titolo: Kid Kool

Anno: 1988

Descrizione: Kid Kool and the Quest for the Seven Wonder Herbs is a video game released for the Nintendo Entertainment System in 1988 by Vic Tokai. The game's main character is based on Kenji Sagara (相良 健治, Sagara Kenji), a popular Japanese child actor who was famous in the 1980s for his impersonation of baseball player Masayuki Kakefu.Kid Kool is also one of the games featured in the Japanese Show GameCenter CX.